step by step plan for chatbot

Define the Purpose –  users with flight status airport info,type of the plane,the how long gnna take and etc
Choose a  Platform – Options: chatgpt ai api,deepseek ai api,gemini ai api.
Think Design,the color,name of the ai, 
Implement Backend Integration add it to the our website which we already made previous semester  Connect to flight APIs to fetch real-time data.
Develop the Frontend Interface – Add a chat widget using JavaScript, HTML, and CSS.
Train and Test the Chatbot – machine learning project tho
Deploy the Chatbot find the host where you can save 
Monitor,Improve and test then finish the project
